### Test Category Controller

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7215/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get all categories (initially empty)
GET {{baseUrl}}/category
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Auto-categorize all receipt items using GPT
POST {{baseUrl}}/category/auto-categorize
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get all categories (after auto-categorization)
GET {{baseUrl}}/category
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get a specific category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/category/CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create a new category manually
POST {{baseUrl}}/category
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

